SELECT pupils.name
FROM pupils
INNER JOIN instructors ON pupils.name = instructors.name
INNER JOIN classes ON instructors.teacher_id = classes.teacher_id
WHERE pupils.end_date = 2025 AND classes.level = 12 AND classes.year >= 2005

SELECT pupils.name
FROM pupils
INNER JOIN instructors ON pupils.name = instructors.name
INNER JOIN classes ON instructors.teacher_id = classes.teacher_id
WHERE pupils.end_date = 2025 AND classes.level = 1
